OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly rain in east Kent
OL,6,Fclearing this morning, leaving a
OL,7,Fbright and chilly start. Cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing, leaving sunny spells and
OL,9,Fshowers, locally heavy, with the risk
OL,10,Fof hail and thunder, during the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Lighter winds than Sunday.
OL,12,FFeeling warmer.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FEarly evening showers fading
OL,15,Fto leave a dry night, with prolonged
OL,16,Fclear spells. Turning chilly, with a
OL,17,Ftouch of frost in prone rural spots.
OL,18,FSome isolated mist and fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
