OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother bright and chilly
OL,6,Fstart, with isolated mist and fog
OL,7,Fpatches soon clearing. Staying dry,
OL,8,Fbut turning increasingly cloudy from
OL,9,Fthe west, during the afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling warm, with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of rain moving east
OL,14,FWednesday, clearing overnight. Windy
OL,15,Fand mild. Sunny spells with fewer and
OL,16,Flighter showers Thursday. Drier and
OL,17,Fbrighter Friday. Feeling warmer with
OL,18,Flight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
